README.md

Awesome

   A curated list of awesome iBeacon and Eddystone Bluetooth beacon
   resources, open source projects, libraries, tools and tutorials. This
   repo is part of the [http://developers.beaconinside.com/]Beacon
   Developer Hub project.

Eddystone by Google

     Eddystone A platform for marking up the world to make your apps and
     devices work smarter by providing timely, contextual information.

     * [https://developers.google.com/beacons/]Google Developers Beacons
       Portal
     * [https://github.com/google/eddystone]Eddystone Protocol
       Specification & Tools
     * Advertising frame types
          + [https://github.com/google/eddystone/tree/master/eddystone-uid
            ]Eddystone-UID
          + [https://github.com/google/eddystone/tree/master/eddystone-tlm
            ]Eddystone-TLM
          + [https://github.com/google/eddystone/tree/master/eddystone-url
            ]Eddystone-URL
     * [https://github.com/google/eddystone/tree/master/tools/eddystone-va
       lidator]Eddystone Validator
     * [Eddystone GATT Configuration Service & Google Nearby API and
       Proximity API](*
       [https://github.com/NordicSemiconductor/Android-nRF-Beacon-for-Eddy
       stone]) (by Nordic Semiconductor)
     * [https://beaufortfrancois.github.io/sandbox/web-bluetooth/eddystone
       -url-config/]Web Bluetooth Eddystone Configurator
     * [https://github.com/google/eddystone/tree/master/branding]Eddystone
       Branding Guidelines &
       [https://github.com/google/eddystone/tree/master/branding/assets]Lo
       gos

Physical Web

     The Physical Web is an approach to unleash the core superpower of
     the web: interaction on demand. People should be able to walk up to
     any smart device - a vending machine, a poster, a toy, a bus stop, a
     rental car - and not have to download an app first. Everything
     should be just a tap away.

     * [http://google.github.io/physical-web/]Physical Web - Walk up and
       use anything - Official Github repository
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w0XazPrh7r0]Video: Introduction to
       the Physical Web - Ubiquity Dev Summit 2016
     * [https://beaufortfrancois.github.io/sandbox/physical-web/url-valida
       tor/]URL Validator 1, [https://url-caster.appspot.com/webui]URL
       Validator 2
     * [https://docs.google.com/document/d/1VC9umaw9TItV31WrcX0eJ9xVsfXXQo
       WvUjuSqWXmH8A]Physical Web Getting Started Guide for Developers
     * [https://github.com/google/physical-web/blob/master/implementation-
       status.md]Physical Web Implementation Status
     * [https://github.com/google/physical-web/blob/master/documentation/b
       randing_guidelines.md]Physical Web Branding Guidelines &
       [https://github.com/google/physical-web/tree/master/documentation/i
       mages/logo]Logos
     * [https://web.eecs.umich.edu/%7Eprabal/teaching/resources/eecs582/wa
       nt15iot.pdf]IEEE: Enabling the Internet of Things by R. Want, B.
       Schilit, S. Jenson
     * [https://medium.com/@urish/exploring-the-physical-web-without-buyin
       g-beacons-efae51e36c2e]Exploring the Physical Web (Without Buying
       Beacons)

Proximity Beacon API by Google

     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0QeY9FueMow]Beacons 101-- Getting
       Started with the Google Beacon Platform - Video Ubiquity Dev Summit
       2016
     * [https://developers.google.com/beacons/get-started]Get Started with
       Beacons - This guide explains the steps required to start using
       Bluetooth low energy (BLE) beacons to provide proximity-based
       experiences for your users.
     * [https://developers.google.com/beacons/proximity/guides]Proximity
       Beacon API - A cloud service that allows you to manage data
       associated with your BLE beacons using a REST interface
     * [https://developers.google.com/nearby/]Nearby - Build simple
       interactions between nearby devices and people

iBeacon Resources by Apple

     iBeacon for Developers From welcoming people as they arrive at a
     sporting event to providing information about a nearby museum
     exhibit, iBeacon opens a new world of possibilities for location
     awareness, and countless opportunities for interactivity between iOS
     devices and iBeacon hardware.

     * [https://developer.apple.com/ibeacon]iBeacon for Developers
     * [https://developer.apple.com/ibeacon/Getting-Started-with-iBeacon.p
       df]Getting Started with iBeacon (PDF)
     * [https://developer.apple.com/ibeacon/]iBeacon Artwork and
       Specifications
     * [https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT202880]iOS: Understanding
       iBeacon device compatibility
     * [https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201357]iOS 7: Understanding
       Location Services
     * [https://developer.apple.com/library/ios/samplecode/AirLocate/Intro
       duction/Intro.html]Apple AirLocate Sample Code
       ([http://stackoverflow.com/questions/26079530/apple-airlocation-dem
       o-app-ranging-not-shows-beacons]iOS8 fix)
     * [https://developer.apple.com/library/ios/documentation/userexperien
       ce/conceptual/LocationAwarenessPG/LocationAwarenessPG.pdf]Location
       and Maps Programming Guide (PDF)

iBeacon for Developers

     * [http://shop.oreilly.com/product/0636920033813.do]Building
       Applications with iBeacon
     * [http://www.cisco.com/c/dam/en/us/solutions/collateral/enterprise-n
       etworks/connected-mobile-experiences/ibeacon_faq.pdf]Cisco iBeacon
       FAQ
     * [https://www.thoughtworks.com/insights/blog/what-is-ibeacon-in-5-mi
       nutes]5 Minute Overview - What is iBeacon? by ThoughtWorks
     * [https://www.thoughtworks.com/insights/blog/semi-technical-lowdown-
       working-ibeacons]A Semi-Technical Lowdown on Working with iBeacons
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0IGeQqEGhx4]CapTech Webinar:
       iBeacon Demystified
     * [http://developer.radiusnetworks.com/2014/01/10/ibeacon-misconcepti
       ons.html]5 fundamental misconceptions about Beacon technology by
       RadiusNetworks
     * [http://mashable.com/2014/05/09/beacons-limitations/]Ask a Dev:
       What Are the Limitations of Beacons?
     * [http://mashable.com/2014/02/24/beacons-geofencing-location/]What's
       the Difference Between Beacons and Geofencing?
     * [http://beekn.net/guide-to-ibeacons/]Guide to iBeacon Hardware by
       beekn.net
     * [http://beekn.net/developing-ibeacon-app/]Developing an iBeacon App
       by beekn.net

Hacks & Cool Apps

     * [https://www.wayfindr.net/]Empowering vision impaired people to
