     * [https://github.com/tmwagency/Glasstimote]Google Glass & Beacons
     * [http://blog.twocanoes.com/post/68861362715/10-awesome-things-you-c
       an-do-today-with-ibeacons]10 awesome things you can do today with
       iBeacons (by Twocanoes)
     * [https://github.com/panicinc/PunchClock]PunchClock An in/out
       tracking app for iOS 7+ that uses iBeacon and Geofencing.
     * [https://github.com/LocativeHQ/ios-app]The Geofancy iOS app Helping
       you to get the best out of your automated home, geofencing,
       iBeacons at your hand.
     * [http://launchhere.awwapps.com/]LaunchHere for iOS - iBeacon based
       app shortcuts
     * [https://medium.com/@urish/traveling-with-beacons-checked-luggage-m
       ade-easy-bbd664765ea3]Traveling with Beacons: Checked Luggage Made
