       iBeacon Problem

Beacon Discovery & Configuration Tools

     * [https://github.com/RadiusNetworks/scanbeacon-gem]ScanBeacon - A
       ruby gem that allows you to scan for beacon advertisements using
       IOBluetooth (on Mac OS X) or a BlueGiga BLE112 device (on mac or
       linux)

